beer.beer_description:
Lusty, resinous and balanced Martian IPA, it balances malt sweetness with potent new world hops that send your taste buds spinning like a UFO!
With its bold and rich taste, this brew is sure to satisfy any beer lover's craving for something unique and delicious. So why not take a sip, sit back, and let your taste buds blast off to the red planet.
